doc.field: I needed a bite before heading over to Bottom of the Hill for some good ol' San Francisco rock and roll.
Mars Bar stops serving food at 8pm, so Betsy, Alison and I had to go elsewhere for a bite. That place ended up being the nearby I Heart Sushi & Teriyaki. Suck it, Mars Bar.
